values:
hmm so it's been quite some time .. 

i don't even know whats happened it's been so long .. let's see ..

spring break came and went .. it kinda sucked cuz it was so early.

softball season is in full swing now .. i love the girls and with the exception of one little glitch we all get along, but at least we all agree on that one glitch haha.  it's not the same as last year but at least we get along quite a bit better.  i cant wait for our campoutt haha.  except we lost to freakin shawnee today so im pretty pissed off from that .. oh well.

umm lets see .. got fired/let go from work until softball is over, which really sucks because i need money badly, but oh well.

umm .. i went to three colleges last weekend- towson, shippensburg, n william paterson.  towson sucked, but it was soo much fun because bek came with me, and it's always too much fun when the two of us are together.  I loved ship, but i'm kinda too smart for there.  but they have a really good journalism department so i'm gonna keep that as a safety school in case everything else fails.  william paterson just sucked.  i really don't wanna go to school in nj, but i went just to please my dad.  it was the biggest waste of an absolutely gorgeous afternoon that i could have spend tanning.  blahh.

i think thats it .. 

41 days left til summer!!
4 months and 3 days til wildwood!!

so this has really been the week from hell.  these past few weekends, last weekend especially, have been amazing, so i should have known it was coming.

Let's see .. where to even begin? I had scrimmage 4 everys, none of which I can really remember because it was so incredibly cold this week.  I think we went 1-3.  haha yea not cool.  I think we're gonna be pretty good once we all pull together and get used to playing with each other.  At least better than last year.  Anyways, I think that softball in March should be outlawed.  The weather is absoultely ridiculous.

My grades in school SUCK.  I don't know when I decided to stop caring, but I definitely have.  Not good.  I need to finish out this year semi-strong to get the hell outta here and into college.

Work.  Blah.  I definitely need to pick up more hours (wait til later to hear why ..) and I just don't have the time.  I want a car soooooooo bad, but I don't have any time to work.  Just between softball and school alone is hard to find time to work, but soon i'm gonna have to visit more colleges and go down the shore for a few weekends.

And on to today, possibly the worst day ever.  I went into it thinking that it would be a good day .. I mean, friday, half day, it all sounded good.  Wrong.  Softball game an hour away, so I had to be back at CHS by 2:30, which kills a half day.  The game was okay, until about the bottom of the first inning when the bases were loaded.  The infield was in, and BAMB! Bomb right into my left ankle.  Yeah, it hurt.  Then we lost.  So I got home at like 6:30.  I really wanted to see my boyfriend bc i only get to see him like once a week and i miss him, :( but that just didnt work out, so i decided to have a blockbuster night with alyssa and neen.  We made it about half way down my steet when I hit a fucking parked car with my mirror.  Yeah, that was the end of that.  Thank God they didnt want to call the insurance company or anything .. now I just have to pay for two new mirrors .. one for their car, and one for mine, which leads to why i need more hours, but dont have the time to work them.  This whole fucking accident pushes back when i get my own car bc i need money, and now i have to regain the trust of my parents.  i really hope they let me out tomorrow night because I need to get out of the house and see matt.

hmm i had a lot to say.  i guess that's what happens when you're stuck at home on a friday night.

okay so we were supposed to have a scrimmage tomorrow but it got cancelled bc the fields are a bit flooded from all the snow.

thats messed up.  it's march.  the snow should be long gone.


so i hung out with the old "group" tonight .. we talked about all our middle school memories .. it seems like all that was so long ago.  it's hard to believe that a little over a year from now we'll be coming back from college and sharing those stories again .. wow thats a really scary thought! anyways i had fun and i miss u guys!

62 days til summer!
not that im counting or anything.

so softball finally started .. n i've seriously never been in so much pain before .. i dont kno why everything hurts this badly.

this weekend was fun tho!! fri nite me n dana drove around then went over beks, where we had a water fight in her kitchen.  i got pinned down by dana as bek poured a cup of water on me.  yes it was great.  after an 8 am practice and 6 hours of work i went over matts .. then after sleeping til 11:30, writing an essay in an hr, then going back to bed until 3, i went to work, and here i am now.  lovely.

hmm thats about it. I got my hours totally cut back in work, so i'm only workin thurday night, which means that i'm gonna have another fun weekend coming up .. yay!!

wow .. fun night lol

hmm let's see .. long four day .. n then we got more stupid snow, which meant a delayed opening .. yeah no complaining there .. except theres a nor'easter on the way, and im gonna cry if we get the two feet of snow they said we could get.

one week til softball!!!

lets see .. thursday night i had work til 9 .. then i just went home n chilled out bc i was still kinda sick, and i figured that i'd go out fri, sat, n sunday night, but then drew asked me if i could work til 10 friday night, so i figured ok, ill be nice and do them a favor and i would still be able to go out saturday and sunday night .. 

friday night i watched the notebook when i came home .. it was soo good!! i didnt cry tho .. i guess cuz i knew what was comin cuz i read the book .. 

Anyways saturday was fun .. i didnt have to work at all, so me and rob went to matt's game in the afternoon .. then i went with bek, matt, n some of his friends to some other bball game (yes, i made it thru two bball games in one day .. be proud of me!) n after that game me n bek went to visit dana at work then went back to her house .. it was funn!!

bek was just a little insane last nite .. never, ever let her have cough medicine.  I stopped the car and almost made her get out .. yeahh .. TROLL!!! ear hair .. stupid questions ..

so i had work today n then i was plannin on goin out with matt n dana .. but NOOOOOOO! it has to freakin snow ... boo!!!

oh well .. so nothing ever goes the way its planned .. at least i have tomorrow off .. i just have to write an essay, then i'll probably catch up in the oc .. woo hoo!!

i miss you :(

wow so this had to have been like the worst valentines day ever ..

it was a rainy, cold monday .. i was sick .. i had work .. but alyssa was a good valentine!! haha 

the weekend was fun tho .. hung out with matt friday n saturday .. went to wildwood for the day sunday .. but now i really cant wait for summer .. oh well.

so i officially suck at school.

(marking period 1 + marking period 2 + exam = semester)
history- A + B + B = B
creative writing- A + A + A = A
algebra 2- B + A + B = B
spanish 4- B + B + B = B
chemistry- B + A + B = B
english- C + A + A = B

soo yea obviously the only thing I'm good at is reading or writng, and i love how everything i do is really starting to prove it. I just wish i tried first marking period so that I would have A's all across the board.  I'm really gonna work my ass off the second half of the year because it's still possible for me to get an A for the year, and I really wanna do it.

I've never seen so many B's in my life.  This is gonna kill my gpa.  Hey, no C's thought.  

Haha I didn't get sociology back yet.  There's still time.

Argg I have work every night this weekend!!!! I need somethin to do after it today tho .. too bad that there's nothing!!

hmm .. not too bad of weekend, i guess.

fri nite- me n bek were bad kids n snuck out to audubon haha .. it was fun .. except we left at like 10:45 n bek had to be home at 11 so i was goin 80mph on 295 n like 60mph on 70 .. n i got bek in right at 11!! hell yeahh! lol.

sat- i had work from 11:30-6 but i got to leave at like 4:30 but my cars were already snowed in and my neighbor n my dad came to get me at like 5:30 .. yeahh.  i had to stay home sat night which totally sucked because i was soo bored and just wanted to drive around and whatnot

sunday- snow slut, whore, n bitch!! fun day with alyssa .. we walked to the lake, which was frozen, so hung out on the dock in the snow .. then we went back to her house n went in her hottub n smores .. then back to my house for the eagles game n some hardcore studying.

tomorrow- lisa and alyssa's snow day #2!! hopefully we'll get to go sledding! i love sleddin!!

and maybe somewhere in there i'll find some time to study .. maybe.

yeahh its been awhile ..

life=busy.  School is nuts, especially with midterms, and i started workin, which is two nights a week n on weekends, and the weather just SUCKS!!! These past two days were the only days ive seen the sun in like a month .. n now we're gonna get like a blizzard saturday night .. why not sunday night? c'mon we might as well miss school cuz of it .. oh well.

weekend night have been fun because I get the car now .. haha yess girls we've had some fun n crazy times .. gettin lost, almost hittin a deer .. wow lol.

hmmm i need somewhere to go tonite!!!!

wow i cant believe that there's only one day left of winter break ..

New Years was fun .. didn't party, get drunk, or do anythin crazy, but still had fun.  I didnt have anyone to kiss at midnite tho :( .. did get a phone call tho .. n it wasnt from kyle haha .. bek n jill- "hook a hottie" .. yeahh fun times!

Alyssa came over .. we watched parts of Napoleon Dynamite again .. wow thats such a great movie .. "I'm waiting for u to leave ur house so i can steak you and orange ur car!" "Flippin' idiots!" But definitely the best part ever- "Can I have your tots?" .. especially funny while watchin it with my parents n eating tots lol. then we partied in my hottub .. yes i kno ur jealous .. n u should be!

merry belated christmas.

so my christmas kinda sucked.  I'm sure if i was given a car it would have been the best christmas ever, but not everyones that lucky.  For me, it was a day of spending time with people that you don't give a rats ass about.  Sad, but oh so true.

This is definitely gonna be the worst winter break ever.  I can't wait to go to college so I appreciate coming back to marlton, because right now it sucks.

Pretty uneventful weekend .. it wasn't a bad one tho! haha .. 

First snow of the season last night .. yuck!! i hate snow! And then today it was like 11 degrees in the morning n then the windchill .. i'm seriously still cold from the bus stop this morning .. i was still like shaking during 2nd period .. it was nuts.  I've decided that I'm going south for college.  Now that I have the choice, I'm not stickin around here with this cold weather.

Jingle Ball- Absolutely amazing night!

Highlights
-Bek's burnt chicken stench
-Bowling for Soup beer break #1
-Bowling for Soup beer break #2
-"Which one's Chingy?"

And by far the best highlight of the night- Ryan Cabrera

Oh my fucking God.  He's amazing.

He's not the world's hottest guy, but he is so damn sexy.  Besides playin the guitar, he kicks ass at the drums .. that was one of the hottest things ive ever see .. wow .. "only a true man can wear pink snowman socks ... and scooby doo boxers!" He's such an awesome performer .. when he comes to Philly by himself I'm definitely going.

And meeting him!! Wow he's so adorable!! He's so tiny! lol .. i told him that his performance was awesome n he's like .. "oh thanks sweetie! it was fun!" and then he gave me a hug .. Ahh he called me sweetie!!!!!!!!!! And he hugged me!!!!!!!!! It was sooooooo amazing!!!!!!!!!!!!

I seriously hate Marlton and CHS.  School sucks, and there's nothing to do on the weekends.  The only thing that Marlton actually has is the movies .. there are like four malls nearby, but they're a pain in the ass to get to, and theres a bowlin alley down 73.  And thats it.  I can't wait to get out of here.  Yeah, it's a great place to raise kids and its safe and blah blah blah .. but its sooo dull.  And it seems like it rain almost every friday nite, so I can never drive anywhere then.  On top of this, it doesn't help that I live in the Goddamn middle of nowhere.

At least its almost Christmas break.  That'll give me 10 days to catch up on my sleep.  Last year I was a freakin insomniac.  Not only could I not sleep, but I didn't need it.  I'm definitely paying for that this year.  Sleep is the most amazing thing ever, but there's just not enough time for it.  At least not with the homework and papers I get.  Somehow I have to start and finish three papers within the next two weeks, along with all my other homework and tests.  It's definitely gonna be a tough time before break.

The worst thing about the holidays is not having a boyfriend.  I have no one that'll spend $130 on me. :( .. alright, yea thats just a little crazy, but i have no one.  I think Christmas is lonelier than valentines day.  I dunno .. they both suck.

Enough whining.  This is what rainy days do to me.

thanksgiving is a really stupid holiday .. i guess it would be better if i liked my family .. yeahhh .. 

So i started my christmas shopping .. its kinda hard to shop when you're like totally broke .. i applied to another place today because i desperately need a job .. i got something for bek already .. her present is amazing .. i'm totally clueless of what to get rob.

i'm quite depressed that i'm not gonna have a boyfriend for christmas. :( oh well .. i guess there are worse things .. thats why i can't wait to go to college and meet some guys .. the guys here suckkk

jingle ball december 13th!!!! omg i cant wait!! we're gonna have so much fun!!! ryan cabrera <33333333

Homecoming weekend .. 

CHS playoff football game friday nite .. we lost to township 12-14 .. oh well .. always next year .. it was a fun time tho hangin out with the new n improved gang haha

Soccer championship game saturday morning .. we won!! yeahhh green slime!! great season girls .. thanx for teachin me how to play!

After the game I just chilled for a little bit then picked dana up .. we went to walmart to get crap to make shirt for spirit day .. then we got ready for homecomin n took pictures and shit .. the dance sucked sooo badly .. maybe it was cuz i need a bf? who knows .. after was fun tho .. we went to fridays then me and dana slept over nicoles and made our shirts today .. they look hott 

Highlights of the weekend
-Nicole patting the wrong kids head
-Before and after the dance
-Me not willing to steal at Walmart
-Turnin out the lights at the Chinese place

Yeah that doesnt seem like much but it was fun!!

We went on a field trip to the state house to film some show for njn .. seriously whenever we're on camera it's gonna be me and bek in the back laughin .. first we just started laughin for the hell of it .. then she dropped her sticker so we just started laughin even harder .. haha

Highlights of the Field Trip
-Beks sticker
-Playing with the toys
-The desire to play hide n seek in the state house
-Dan
-The desire to get with the gay kid
-Our list on the bus
-The twitching horse

But our day wasn't over .. me, bek, and my sis drove around a lil bit .. i had to get matt a card, then we looked at some shoes, then we went tanning .. woo hoo!! yea bek thats what havin a license is about .. we gotta do it again!

I got a stupid 89 in chem .. if i did the second extra credit i would of had an A.  That makes me mad.

And my 78 in english.  Yea i gotta stop before I get started.

I got a cheap tan today! My face is burnt! I love it!

Wow me and bek are talkin about things we're not supposed to be talkin about .. we're so bad!

Another weekend, another college .. I went to the University of Delaware today .. it was gorgeous! It's a bigger school, but its so cute .. and its right in town and there's a mainstreet with shops and clubs right outside of it and you can walk everywhere .. i love it!

me and alyssa hung out with her cats! (eww!) yea we can't wait for christmas because we love the music .. but we want boyfriends this year :(
haha the gangsterr xmas rap .. wow

yea so this loser named smithers sits behind me in math and throws paper in my hair .. uncool.

i get to sleep in tomorrow! wow majorly excited .. haha

Only I would visit three colleges and fall in love with the only one that i couldnt get into.  I mean, I only need my SAT score to be at least a 1300.  Who am I kiddin?

Rutgers is just too big.  It's spread out over 3 cities and you need to take a bus to get to your classes and all.  Great school and I could get into it, but its just too damn big.  And they only have a five year education program, which is my backup.

Rowan's nice, but it's too close to home.  That might be my safety school because I kno i can get into it and i like the majors.  With any major you chose, writing is emphasized which i really liked.

TCNJ.  Omg I fell in love with it .. amazing journalism program on top of everything else.  The campus is absolutely gorgeous.  I was so set on goin out of state, but this is far away enough where i'm out on my own.  I even had a squirrel jump out at me- just like at home .. If I get above a 1300 thats where i'm goin.  hah.

I must say that rowan had the best guys .. esp the guy at the pool .. wow good times

Alyssa, neen and I partied in the car today!!! Jackass!! Fuck yeahh!! and our interesting convo on orgasms .. woooahh!! haha yea it was quite amusing! we stopped at wawa to get icees to drink as we watched the sexy chad michael murray in a cinderella story again.  ahh he gets me every time!

Thank God it's a 4 day weekend .. not like i'll be doin too much, tho.  Tomorrow i get to sleep in!!!! yeah im soo excited about that!! haha .. then i'll probably wind up hanging with alyssa again.  Friday the college search begins .. ahhh!!! My dad and I are goin to Rutgers at like 7am .. he'd better be in a half decent mood or its gonna be the day from hell.  Saturday I have the SATs in the morning (AHHHH!!!!!) followed by visitin tcnj, which i can never get into.  Sunday i'm goin to stockton.  I don't even wanna go in nj.  I'm just doin this to please the parents.  rutgers, rowan, and stockton are my back up schools.  I wonder which one i'll wind up at.

yeahh so long busy weekend .. wish me luck!!

I'm so jealous of alyssa because she has friends who have hot older brothers .. none of my friends have hot older brother .. c'mon, guys .. cant you even try to help me out??? 

Yeah so Halloween really sucks when you get older.  I did homework, filled out job applications, and handed out candy today.  Woohoo.  Altho neen did bring me home a good amount of candy. :D

A group of guys dressed up as girls n cheerleaders came to my door and hit on me.  Lemme tell yah what an experience that was.

Yeahhh red sox .. kinda late, but whatever.

I've had a rly fun weekend! 

Friday I saw The Grudge with Bek, Rob and Rob .. it was a pretty good movie. I didn't think it was as scary as a lot of people did, but that lil Chinese kid was rly creepy.  

SAT class today .. then me and dana went shoppin!! I got my homecomin dress!! it's rly cute .. its strapless and dark purple .. it's somethin different than i thought i'd get but i rly like it .. i just gotta get rid of the flower.  Then we had a girls night out for Nicole's birthday.  Me, Nicole, Bek, Dana, and jess went bowling .. it was fun!!

Oh yeah .. I'm so effin pissed off about the whole car situation.  I understand that my parents dont want me to get my own car right away because they want me to get more experience, but theyve only let me take the car about by myself once since I got my license.  I dont kno how im gonna get experience before i get my car if they dont let me have it at all.  I kno that ive only had my license for almost like 2 weeks, but i thought i was gonna get a lil time with it.  It's really pissin me off and i got in a huge fight with them about it.  They just dont understand how hard it is to live in a town like Marlton and not have a car waiting in the driveway on my 17th birthday.  I've been handling it pretty well, but when they dont even let me use their car its gettin to me.

I guess thats it .. i'm applying to kohls because i need to start bringin in some money so i can hurry up and get my own car!!

Another weeks dragging by .. Like i can't believe it's already the end of October, but each week goes by so damn slow.  School is hell.  It's just so much work.  All I wanna do it get a job so i can get a car n get the hell outta marlton n meet some boys!!!

lys- u crack me up .. lookin thru my yearbook n at the graph paper .. wow.

i finally got to drive today!!! haha .. my parents are like so scared to let me drive bc some people in my neighborhood are morons and go 55mph down the street and crash into trees .. yeahh thats not too cool.

so today i had psats, which sucked, not that i expected anythin else.  Then i drove bek home .. the best feeling in the world is drivin urself somewhere .. its awesome.  then i did my history project n just hung out .. then my alyssa came over!! haha ive missed her!! we watched mean girls and got depressed bc we need bfs .. or at least some action haha .. oh well.

GUESS WHO GOT HER LICENSE??????????????????

oh yes, i'm armed and dangerous.

What an awesome weekend .. even tho friday nite didnt go as planned, the next two days were soo amazin ..

saturday- MY BIRTHDAY!!!

Me n bek hung out at my house for a lil .. she gave me my present!!! i love bob the healthy cow!!!! haha .. then we played nintendo and she got stared at by neen's bunny slipper n we fed alyssa's cats .. i made bek clean up the crap ..

That afternoon bek and i went down the shore .. hour n a half car ride there .. bek was on the phone with kyle n then shes like .. "he's gotta tell ya somethin" so i took the phone n all i hear from his is "i'm only wearin a towel." kinda scary.

then like the second we got in the house me n neen starting fightin lol.  but then we went out for dinner n out and around the wood.  wow- i must say that i LOVE the wood!! we got hit on n checked out by some guys .. the bus boys .. hairy scary monster!!! u cant take the chips!! random kids on the boardwalk .. we saw the funniest thing ever on the boards- there was a guy sittin on a bench wearin headphones and sunglasses singing/screaming the same song over and over again .. "if this isn't love .. let me kno!!!" omgg it was soo freakin funny!! Then we saw him ridin his bike down the boards singin it .. wow.  We did the go karts .. me n bek killed everyone! we kept gettin yelled at for bumpin people and cuttin people off tho .. No screamin on the go karts!!! We saw the greatest shirt .. "If you see da police .. warn-a-brother" .. 

then we went back to my house .. we were in the upstairs apartment n we were lookin in my fridge n bek was like "wow ur dad rly trusts u with alcohol in the house" n i was like "what? theres nothin in here!!" i was totally oblivious to the freakin 12 pack right in front of me.

kyle called us n woke us up at 1:15am to say that he saw scared because he was walkin home from his friends house n it was foggy n there was a ditch and a bunch of white people .. odd kid .. he must have called at least 55 times over the weekend .. im not kiddin either

we woke up this mornin to find it nice n sunny .. so we ate breakfast n got our swimsuits on to go to the beach .. but then we looked outside to see it all cloudy, so we decided to go for a bike ride .. we wound up on the boardwalk, which we werent supposed to be bc its pretty far from my house .. and well, three girls in the wood probably isnt the smartest idea.  At the end of the boardwalk is a shoe store that was havin a huuuuuuuuge sale .. all 3 of us got rly cute flip flops, but we had a problem .. we needed to find a way to get em home .. whatever our logic was didn't work for bek .. the bag hit the wheel n she almost flew over the handle bars .. after neen crashed in the cvs parking lot, we made it home.

By that time, the sun was out so we went to the beach .. but on the way there, neens brand new flip flop broke and she fell on the sidewalk .. amazing .. then i saw the timberweed roll by .. the beach was awesome, especially for october .. we just hung out, tanned, hand a catch, and skimboarded.  there was a really fat lady there and her flip flops started floating away so i saved one and bek saved the other and she gave bek a rly dirty look and was like "how did my flip flop get there?" umm duhh the freakin tide took it away u bitch!!"

It eventually got cold there so we went back to the house and took another bike ride, which was even more funfilled than the first .. the one bike that bek and neen had to take turns ridin was my mom's bike back when she was our age (haha i was too short for it) so its one of those hunch back bikes .. lets just say that they had problems with it .. bek almost got run over while ridin the death bike by some lady who called her a jerk .. neen dropped her icee a few times .. n i lost count at the number of times they fell off .. the best time bek fell was when she skimmed the curb while some guy was checkin us out.

there was some guy on the ride home n that had like bulgin eyes n was gawking at us .. scary

So now beks over n theres still time to cause some more trouble .. hell, my weekends only half over ..

2 days til my license!!!!!
i love bob the healthier cow and the wood!!!

So tonite didn't turn out exactly as planned .. but some parts were pretty good .. haha yeaahhhh .. so anyways this weekend is gonna be amazing!!!!! Lets see .. tomorrow- my bday n me n bek are goin to wildwood .. we're just gonna hang out n stir up some trouble saturday and sunday .. then monday i get the house to myself bc the kids have school n i dont!!!!! woo .. party at my house!!!! haha how awesome would that be? then tuesdays the big day .. 2pm at winslow- AHHHH!!! Haha i should do pretty well .. i cant wait!!!!

Less than an hour til i turn 17!!!!!! I feel old!!!

loooong day .. there's still to much drama

birthday: 5 days
license: 8 days

chris got his license today- congrats!!

Hmm .. quite a lot has happened since last weekend .. too much drama this week .. yeahh waaaay too much drama .. but whatever, it's all crap.
